# Note Taking App

#this Flutter project serves as a simple Note Taking App.

## Features
- Create and edit notes, allowing to make bulet points and item checklist
- Save notes locally
- Simple and intuitive user interface
-importing photo
- able to minimise and maximize the font size
-drawing feature

## IDE Used
This project was created using Intellij IDEA

##built with
- flutter run

## Getting Started
To run this project locally, follow the steps below:

### Installation Requirements
1. Verify that you have Flutter installed. If not, [install Flutter](https://flutter.dev/docs/get-started/install).
2. Install dependencies using `flutter pub get`.
3. Run the app using `flutter run`.

#Usage:
## Usage
- Open the app.
- Create a new note by tapping the '+' button.
- Edit your notes.
- add bullet points
-add item checklist

#running Pubspec.yaml
to fetch the project dependencies you will need to run the following command in the terminal:

 - flutter pub get

to upgrade the flutter
- flutter upgrade

to verify SDK version matches the version specified in pubspec.yaml run:
- flutter --version

### Flutter Version Compatibility
This project is built with Flutter version 3.16.5
Make sure that your Flutter SDK version matches or is newer.
